author: slessard
msg: TRINIDAD-716 Changed Icon.renderIcon signature to be more flexible and allow Map<String, ? extends Object> attribute map. This change should not break backward compatibility and allow to call the method using Map<String, String> that get returned from Collections.singletonMap("key", "value"), potentially improving the performances of code using such map instances.
